headline: Encompass Health Beats Q1 Earnings Estimates, Ups '25 EPS View
summary: EHC's Q1 results benefit on the back of discharge growth and expansion endeavors, partly offset by high operating costs. It currently expects 2025 adjusted EPS from continuing operations within $4.85-$5.10.
